{{Vgname|龙腾世纪：起源|en=Dragon Age: Origins|cn=龙腾世纪：起源|tw=闇龍紀元：序章}}是[[BioWare|BioWare]]开发、[[艺电|艺电]]发行的一款[[电子角色扮演游戏|角色扮演游戏]]，为[[龙腾世纪系列|龙腾世纪系列]]首作。游戏于2009年11月在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]及[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]平台发售，同年12月推出[[Mac_OS_X|Mac OS X]]版本。游戏背景设定在深陷内乱的虚构王国费罗登，玩家可为主角选择人类、[[精灵|精灵]]与[[矮人|矮人]]出身，并扮演战士、法师和盗贼三种职业。随着主角加入对抗邪恶势力“{{le|暗裔|Darkspawn}}”的灰袍守护者组织，故事主线围绕消灭暗裔首领大恶魔以终结其入侵展开。

BioWare形容《龙腾世纪：起源》是一部世界观独特的“黑暗[[英雄奇幻|英雄奇幻]]”作品，为该公司前作《[[博德之门系列|博德之门]]》和《[[无冬之夜系列|无冬之夜]]》系列的[[精神续作|精神续作]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dragonage.bioware.com/game/faq/#1.01 |title=1.01. What is Dragon Age: Origins?|publisher=[[BioWare|BioWare]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100130065445/http://dragonage.bioware.com/game/faq |archivedate=2010-01-30 |url-status=dead}}</ref>游戏灵感源自《[[指环王|指环王]]》及《[[冰与火之歌|冰与火之歌]]》，BioWare称其设定介于[[古典奇幻|古典奇幻]]与[[浅度奇幻|浅度奇幻]]之间。游戏开发工作始于2002年，BioWare动用了超过144名配音演员，同时聘请{{le|伊南·祖尔|Inon Zur}}为本作配乐，游戏的[[家用机|家用机]]版本则交由{{le|Edge of Reality|Edge of Reality}}负责移植。

《龙腾世纪：起源》一经发行即广受好评，游戏的故事剧情、背景设定、角色刻画、配乐及战斗系统均获盛赞，各平台版本在游戏评论网站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]皆表现亮眼。<ref name="metacritic.com">{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/dragon-age-origins |title=Dragon Age: Origins for PC Reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|date=2009-11-03|accessdate=2022-01-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20211128010900/https://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/dragon-age-origins|archivedate=2021-11-28|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="metacritic1">{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-3/dragon-age-origins |title=Dragon Age: Origins for PlayStation 3 Reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|date=2009-11-03|accessdate=2022-01-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20211214084153/https://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-3/dragon-age-origins|archivedate=2021-12-14|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="metacritic2">{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/game/xbox-360/dragon-age-origins|title=Dragon Age: Origins for Xbox 360 Reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|date=2009-11-03|accessdate=2022-01-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210909080650/https://www.metacritic.com/game/xbox-360/dragon-age-origins|archivedate=2021-09-09|url-status=live}}</ref>游戏在全球售出超过320万份，后续[[可下载内容|可下载内容]]则售出100万份以上。游戏也收获众多奖项，多家游戏媒体评选其为2009年度游戏和最佳角色扮演游戏。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bestof.ign.com/2009/pc/pc-game-of-the-year.html |title=PC Game of the Year 2009 - Dragon Age: Origins|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100301121432/http://bestof.ign.com/2009/pc/pc-game-of-the-year.html|archivedate=2010-03-01|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.interactive.org/awards/annual_awards.asp?idAward=2010 |title=AIAS Annual Awards  Role-Playing/Massively Multiplayer Game of the Year|publisher=[[互动艺术与科学学会|AIAS]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100713171822/http://www.interactive.org/awards/annual_awards.asp?idAward=2010 |archivedate=2010-07-13|url-status=dead}}</ref>本作自问世以来即被广泛视为史上最佳的角色扮演游戏之一。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://gamingbolt.com/top-98-greatest-video-games-ever-made/10|title=Top 98 greatest video games ever made | Page 10|first=Rohan |last=Philip|publisher=
GamingBolt|date=2013-04-19|accessdate=2022-01-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210908194600/https://gamingbolt.com/top-98-greatest-video-games-ever-made/10|archivedate=2021-09-08|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.polygon.com/features/2017/11/27/16158276/polygon-500-best-games-of-all-time-500-401|title=The 500 best games of all time: 500-401|author=Polygon Staff|publisher=[[Polygon|Polygon]]|date=2017-11-27|accessdate=2022-01-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20211129073524/https://www.polygon.com/features/2017/11/27/16158276/polygon-500-best-games-of-all-time-500-401|archivedate=2021-11-29|url-status=live}}</ref>

BioWare在游戏发布后又陆续推出{{le|龙腾世纪：起源可下载内容|Dragon Age: Origins downloadable content|数个可下载内容}}，[[资料片|资料片]]《{{le|龙腾世纪：起源 - 觉醒|Dragon Age: Origins – Awakening|觉醒}}》则在2010年3月发售。系列续作《[[龙腾世纪II|龙腾世纪II]]》和《[[龙腾世纪：审判|龙腾世纪：审判]]》分别发行于2011年3月和2014年11月。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.joystiq.com/2010/01/29/bioware-says-dragon-age-2-to-look-super-hot/|title=BioWare says Dragon Age 2 to look 'super hot'|first=James |last=Ransom|publisher=[[Joystiq|Joystiq]]|date=2010-01-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150128160239/http://www.joystiq.com/2010/01/29/bioware-says-dragon-age-2-to-look-super-hot/|archivedate=2015-01-28|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref name="DAIreleaseconfirmedGI">{{cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/games/dragon_age_inquisition/b/pc/archive/2014/04/22/dragon-age-inquisition-dated-for-october-in-new-trailer.aspx|title=Dragon Age: Inquisition Dated For October In New Trailer|last=Futter|first=Mike|publisher=[[GameInformer|GameInformer]]|date=2014-04-22|accessdate=2022-01-10|archive-date=2019-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190525055212/https://www.gameinformer.com/games/dragon_age_inquisition/b/pc/archive/2014/04/22/dragon-age-inquisition-dated-for-october-in-new-trailer.aspx|url-status=live}}</ref>BioWare早在本作发行前便计划推出游戏周边商品，包括续作、桌游、小说与漫画，意在将《龙腾世纪》打造为一个全新的系列。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.zam.com/story.html?story=20052 |title=The Future Of Dragon Age: Origins With Mark Darrah|author=Pwyff|publisher=ZAM|date=2009-10-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120224034152/http://www.zam.com/story.html?story=20052 |archivedate=2012-02-24|url-status=dead}}</ref>

